==Military==
The Belgian Armed Forces have about 46,000 active troops. In 2009 the yearly defence budget was $6 billion.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eda.europa.eu/DefenceData |title=Defence Data Portal |publisher=[[European Defence Agency]] |accessdate=June 15, 2011}}</ref> There are four parts: Belgian Land Component, or the Army; Belgian Air Component, or the Air Force; Belgian Naval Component, or the Navy; Belgian Medical Component.

